
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>V-GUARD AI Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #0a192f; color: white; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
        .hero { padding: 60px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #172a45; text-align: center; }
        .profile-img { width: 150px; height: 150px; border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid #64ffda; object-fit: cover; }
        .feature-card { background: #112240; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; height: 100%; border: 1px solid transparent; transition: 0.3s; }
        .feature-card:hover { border-color: #64ffda; transform: translateY(-5px); }
        .feature-card i { font-size: 2rem; color: #64ffda; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .portal-btn { border: 1px solid #64ffda; color: #64ffda; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 10px; display: inline-block; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
    <img src="erwin.jpg" alt="Erwin Sinaga" class="profile-img">
    <h1 class="mt-3">V-GUARD AI</h1>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-4" style="max-width: 600px;">
        <h5>Visi</h5>
        <p>Menjadi pionir keamanan digital berbasis AI yang adaptif untuk menjamin kedaulatan data bisnis global.</p>
        <h5>Misi</h5>
        <p>Memberikan proteksi siber proaktif melalui teknologi deteksi cerdas serta menyederhanakan manajemen keamanan untuk SME melalui dashboard terintegrasi.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<section class="container py-5 text-center">
    <h2 class="mb-5">Fitur Layanan Produk</h2>
    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                <h6>AI Threat Detection</h6>
                <p class="small text-secondary">Deteksi ancaman otomatis 24/7.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
                <h6>Automatic Response</h6>
                <p class="small text-secondary">Mitigasi instan terhadap serangan.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                <h6>Predictive Analysis</h6>
                <p class="small text-secondary">Analisis celah keamanan sistem.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-network-wired"></i>
                <h6>Endpoint Protection</h6>
                <p class="small text-secondary">Keamanan menyeluruh perangkat.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="container text-center pb-5">
    <a href="/portal-klien" class="portal-btn">Portal Klien</a>
    <a href="/admin-dashboard" class="portal-btn">Admin Dashboard</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>
